author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a new hack that's been proposed to your favourite content creators. Most of us spend our time yapping into mics, with all that audio data it seems some people have found a way to get our passwords just from the clicking of our keyboards. How? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Please Mute Your Mic...
